- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper involves function approximation processes and convergence analysis of the algorithm. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses adaptive optimal control using value iteration, which is a common technique in AI for solving Markov decision processes. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper involves function approximation and convergence analysis, which are common topics in neural networks and evolutionary algorithms. 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper deals with optimal control and stability analysis, which are important topics in robotics.
